Welcome to OQCTest’s documentation!

This is Oxford Quantum circuit -> OQC’s string ingestion API documentation done by BIOKU. This documentation provides a detailed and easy to follow development process of the OQC’s string ingestion API. You will be able to get started with cloning this project, get the required dependencies to make the project work on your own local machine and also see a detailed walkthrough of what each unit of the codebase of this project is doing.
